General, slow down.

5
00:01:59,420 --> 00:02:01,000
The soldiers behind can't keep up.

6
00:02:01,020 --> 00:02:02,940
Then tell them to run faster!

7
00:02:03,250 --> 00:02:04,640
Ning Yuanzhou is such a jerk!

8
