373
00:31:26,550 --> 00:31:27,650
or die for me anymore.

374
00:31:41,210 --> 00:31:42,330
Stab 300 times in a row.

375
00:31:42,720 --> 00:31:43,920
Try not to miss the circle.

376
00:31:44,430 --> 00:31:45,160
After you're done,

377
00:31:45,510 --> 00:31:46,300
