446
00:34:38,429 --> 00:34:40,330
You've had a long day. Have a good rest.

447
00:34:40,409 --> 00:34:41,310
I'll go check on Yuan Lu.

448
00:34:42,070 --> 00:34:42,530
Don't worry.

449
00:34:43,199 --> 00:34:44,020
Okay.

450
00:34:51,870 --> 00:34:53,790
